title: Dungeons and Dragons Classics Vol  1 - 4
description:
The classic DC Comics Advanced Dungeons & Dragons series returns to  print for the first time! An ancient evil rises and once again threatens  the Realms, and only a motley band of adventures can stop it. A surly  dwarf warrior and his benevolent centaur companion, a gladiator who  survived the arenas, a fallen paladin, and a timid half-elf must somehow  find a way to work together if the Realms are going to survive the  coming darkness.


Thanks to the original uploader.
